# CI/CD & DevOps Guide

Project: Developer Intelligence Platform

Version: 1.0

Status: Production Ready

---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the Continuous Integration (CI), Continuous Deployment (CD), infrastructure automation, quality gates, release process, and DevOps standards for the Developer Intelligence Platform.

Objectives

• Ensure every code change is tested automatically.

• Maintain production stability.

• Reduce deployment time.

• Improve software quality.

• Enable collaborative development.

• Automate repetitive engineering tasks.

---

# 2. DevOps Philosophy

The project follows DevOps principles.

Core Principles

Automation First

Everything possible should be automated.

Infrastructure as Code

Infrastructure should be reproducible.

Continuous Integration

Every commit should be tested.

Continuous Deployment

Deployment should require minimal manual work.

Observability

Systems should expose metrics, logs and traces.

Security by Default

Security checks are integrated into CI.

