# 17. Deployment Strategy

The application follows a **Progressive Deployment Model** to reduce risk and ensure reliability.

```
Developer
    │
    ▼
Feature Branch
    │
    ▼
Pull Request
    │
    ▼
CI Pipeline
    │
    ▼
Develop Branch
    │
    ▼
Deploy → Staging
    │
    ▼
Smoke Tests
    │
    ▼
Manual Approval
    │
    ▼
Main Branch
    │
    ▼
Production Deployment
```

Deployment Goals:

- Zero downtime
- Automated rollback
- Safe releases
- Fast recovery
- Observable deployments

